        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段變動不大 恒指回吐5點報23472點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段變動不大，恒生指數開市報23472點，跌5點或0.02%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5864點，升5點或0.09%；國企指數以8670點開市，升3點或0.04%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報138.9元，升0.29%；騰訊(00700)開報522元，升0.97%；美團(03690)開報164.7元，升1.11%；京東(09618)開報161.7元，也升0.06%；小米(01810)開報52.2元，升0.97%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">將於今日派成績表的中電控股(00002)則開報64.25元，跌0.31%；發盈警的新世界發展(00017)不跌反升，於競價時段開報4.46元，升0.68%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14727890-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%ae%8a%e5%8b%95%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a7-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%905%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123472%e9%bb%9e",
